race.comment: DE GRANDHOMME (2) won impressively at Geraldton two back before a disappointing run at Belmont last time out. Back to 1000m again now and the inside draw should see him in a handy position in running. Happy to overlook his poor effort last start and he can return to his best. MAGALI MAGIC (3) drops right back in grade today after finishing 1L away in Saturday company at Ascot 12 days ago. She boasts a strong record at this track and trip and Brad Parnham taking the ride is a positive sign. Appears the main danger. MAGNIQUE (1) showed promising signs through her last campaign and looks back in good order judging by her latest trial. Carries the top weight, but she's a classy customer and she'll turn in a bold sight on return. MIGHTY HOSANNA (4) is better than she showed first-up where she dropped right out of contention. Can bounce back. FAVOURITE SONGS (6) is next best.
